    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and your <strong>cinnamon</strong> and cook for 1 min further</p><p>Once browned, add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>,<strong> beef stock</strong>, <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook over a high heat for 4-5 min or until reduced and the lamb is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>lamb ragù</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
