      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>potato discs </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> in a single layer</p><p>Spoon over <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>lamb ragù</strong></p><p>Then add the<strong> aubergine rounds</strong> in a single layer, followed by a final layer of <strong>lamb ragù</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>cheese sauce</strong> and put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until bubbling and golden – this is your <strong>melty Greek-style lamb moussaka</strong></p>",
